author: The Associated Press
description: Reaction to the fatal explosion at an Ariana Grande concert in Manchester, England: "broken. from the bottom of my heart, i am so so sorry. i don't have words." — Ariana Grande, via Twitter. "My thoughts, prayers and tears for all those affected by the Manchester tragedy tonight. I'm sending all my love." — pop star Taylor Swift, via Twitter "Praying for everyone at @ArianaGrande's show" — pop star Katy Perry, via Twitter "Stunned by the news coming in from the UK. my thoughts are with the fans and families at Ariana's Manchester show. Awful" — TV producer, host Ryan Seacrest, via Twitter
title: Reaction to Manchester explosion at Ariana Grande concert
